<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="興福" xml:id="gsz0881a21shiZhiJun"><lb
ed="T" n="0881a21"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0881a21"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName><persName key="A010402">智頵</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0881a22"/><persName key="A010402">釋智頵</persName>者，<placeName key="PL000000002513">中山</placeName>人也。自幼辭親，來<placeName key="PL000000005392"><placeName>五臺山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0881a23"/><placeName>善住閣院</placeName></placeName>，禮<persName key="A009526">賢林</persName>為師，誦經合格，得度。神<lb
ed="T" n="0881a24"/>情爽拔，氣調<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2312"/>高峙，於世資財，少欲知足。糲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2099"/><lb
ed="T" n="0881a25"/>食充腹，麁衣禦寒，餘有寸帛，未甞不濟諸<lb
ed="T" n="0881a26"/>貧病也。遊方參翫，預諸講席。傳《法華》、《維摩》<lb
ed="T" n="0881a27"/>二部，窮源盡理。後挂錫高峯<ptr target="#n3265"/>，息心却掃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2197"/>。<anchor xml:id="beg0881sgsz2"/>距<anchor xml:id="end0881sgsz2"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g2196"/><lb
ed="T" n="0881a28"/><date notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742020967" notAfter-iso="+0821-02-12"><name>元和</name>中</date>，眾辟為<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName>都檢校守僧長<ptr target="#n3281"/>。<persName key="A010402">頵</persName>與<lb
ed="T" n="0881a29"/>時遷徙，固辭不允，遂登此職。後遇歲當饑<pb ed="T" n="0881b" xml:id="T50.2061.0881b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0881b01"/>饉，寺宇蕭條。有<placeName key="PL000000005362">華嚴寺</placeName>，是大聖棲真之所<ptr target="#n3356"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0881b02"/>巡遊者頗眾，供施稀踈，院宇倫巡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2198"/>，例稱不迨，<lb
ed="T" n="0881b03"/>眾請為<placeName key="PL000000005362">華嚴寺</placeName>都供養主<ptr target="#n3377"/>。時德不孤，有<persName key="A009238">法照</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0881b04"/><persName key="A009517">無著</persName>、<persName key="A001755">澄觀</persName>之出世也。當<persName key="A001755">觀<roleName>師</roleName></persName>製《華嚴經疏》<ptr target="#n924"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0881b05"/>海眾雲集，請<persName key="A010402">頵</persName>為講主，日供千僧。十有餘<lb
ed="T" n="0881b06"/>禩<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2199"/>，食無告乏。皆云「有無盡藏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g645"/>之米麪也」，歲<lb
ed="T" n="0881b07"/>久頗見豐盈。有隣院僧<persName key="A010403">義圓</persName>——亦當代之碩德<lb
ed="T" n="0881b08"/>也——，謂<persName key="A010402">頵</persName>久知常住，私有謗言，非平等心，是<lb
ed="T" n="0881b09"/>貪饕者也。夜有神人報<persName key="A010403">圓</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010402">僧長</ref>是千佛<lb
ed="T" n="0881b10"/>之一數也，<ref type="person" target="#A010403">汝</ref>發輕言。若不悔過，當墮惡道。」<lb
ed="T" n="0881b11"/><persName key="A010403">圓</persName>乃詰朝嗚足<ptr type="glossary" target="#g385"/>懺謝<ptr target="#n3378"/>，有茲驗也。<date notBefore-iso="+0840-02-14" key="j20279082030170" notAfter-iso="+0846-04-25">及鍾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2200"/><persName key="A006570">武宗</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0881b12"/>澄汰</date>，<persName key="A010402">頵</persName>遁乎山谷，不捨<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>之化境。未逾<lb
ed="T" n="0881b13"/>歲載，<persName key="A003667">宣宗</persName>即位，勅<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>諸寺度僧五十人<ptr target="#n3379"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0881b14"/>宣供衣帔，山門再辟<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2201"/>。<persName key="A010402">頵</persName>為十寺僧長兼山<lb
ed="T" n="0881b15"/>門都修造供養主。<date from-iso="+0853-02-16" key="j20326592033012" to-iso="+0854-02-04"><name>大中</name>七年</date>，與<persName key="A021693">寰海</persName>遊<placeName key="PL000000005250">臺</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0881b16"/>四眾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g98"/>建無遮，精妙供養<ptr target="#n3380"/>。一月日，乃謂大眾<lb
ed="T" n="0881b17"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010402">吾</ref>欲暫憩微骸，息心斂迹。佐助眾務，<ref type="person" target="#A010402">吾</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0881b18"/>無能為也，付諸俊哲，繼<ref type="person" target="#A010402">吾</ref>遺躅。」乃淨室<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1985"/>安<lb
ed="T" n="0881b19"/>坐而滅，春秋七十七，夏臘五十八云。</p>
<p xml:id="pT50p0881b2001"><lb
ed="T" n="0881b20"/>系曰：僧中職任也，如網之綱，如屋之梁焉！<lb
ed="T" n="0881b21"/>肇自<placeName key="PL000000048176">姚秦</placeName>立正<ptr target="#n3381"/>，<placeName key="PL000000000130">魏</placeName>世推都<ptr target="#n3382"/>，<placeName key="PL000000000139">北齊</placeName>則十統分<lb
ed="T" n="0881b22"/>員<ptr target="#n3383"/>，<placeName key="PL000000000106">唐</placeName>世則僧錄命職<ptr target="#n3384"/>。異乎常所聞者，<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺<lb
ed="T" n="0881b23"/>山</placeName>自<date notBefore-iso="+0785-02-18" key="j20078242015139" notAfter-iso="+0805-02-28"><name>貞元</name>中</date><ptr target="#n3385"/><persName key="A010402">智頵</persName>始封僧長矣！亦猶魚鹽<lb
ed="T" n="0881b24"/>蜃蛤，祈望<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2202"/>守之也。</p>
